MiceADHD showed heightened radial diffusivity (RD) in
the corpus callosum (F(1,20) = 4.8, p = .041), left and
right hippocampus (left: F(1,20) = 5.3, p = .032; right:
F(1,20) = 17.0, p = .001), and right internal capsule (F(1,20) =
